        "INFO: Salah",
        "DESC: • Offer [salah of Ashura eve]([[salah:ashura-eve]])",
        "DESC: • Offer [Tahajjud salah - Salatul layl]([[salah:tahajjud---salatul-layl]])",
        "INFO: Ziyarah / Dua",
        "DESC: • Recite [Ziyarah Ashura]([[ziyarah:ziyarat-al-ashura]])",
        "DESC: • Recite [Dua Alqama]([[duas:dua-alqama-(safwan)---after-ziyarat-ashura]])"
    ]
}